#: content/project/visual-changelogs/visualchangelog212/index.md:80
msgid "Feature: Ongoing improvements to code quality"
msgstr ""

#: content/project/visual-changelogs/visualchangelog212/index.md:82
msgid ""
"Through the use of the address sanitizer library, hundreds of memory leaks "
"have been identified and fixed. Automated code scans using Coverity Scan "
"have been regularly used to identify potential issues, and our Coverity "
"defect density is now impressively low at just 0.02 defects per 1000 lines "
"of code. The library of automated unit tests has also grown significantly "
"during 2.12, resulting in more regressions being identified and fixed "
"immediately. In 2.12 we also added continuous testing on OSX, so that every "
"commit is tested against the unit test suite on both Linux and OSX "
"platforms."
msgstr ""

