msgstr ""

#: content/project/visual-changelogs/visualchangelog212/index.md:148
msgid ""
"You can now define custom variables for use in expressions. Variables can be"
" defined at the application global level, project level, layer level and "
"composition level. Just like CSS cascading rules, variables can be "
"overwritten - eg, a project level variable will overwrite any application "
"level variables set. You can use these variables to build text strings or "
"other custom expressions. For example in composer creating a label with this"
" content:"
